original: Larsson, Lars Einar Douglas, tandläkare, Uddevalla, f. 22/11/06 i Uddevalla av Lans L. o. Klara Elisabeth Andersson. — Stud :ex. i Uddevalla 26. tandhkand. 29, tandläk. 31. Praktik i Uddevalla sed. 32.
translated: Larsson, Lars Einar Douglas, dentist, Uddevalla, born on November 22, 1906, in Uddevalla to Lans L. and Klara Elisabeth Andersson. - Studied dental medicine in Uddevalla, graduated in 1926, obtained dental degree in 1929, and became a dentist in 1931. Started practicing in Uddevalla since 1932. Please note that '\d\d m. partners name' indicates that the person got married in the year 19xx.
